				\begin{document}$$ {RK}_{S\to {ID}_{VPP}} $$\end{document} is directly generated by the DER agent, without the need for DER generation and forwarding to the DER agent. The SKS required in the re-encryption key generation algorithm is issued and obtained by the verification organization in the Step 1. After generating RKSâIDVPP\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
